  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19 and influenza point of care testing results: how to report
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Notifications of COVID-19 and influenza point of care testing (POCT) results: legal duties for providers of POCT.     </p>

  </div>
</div>

